12) Create "Cost Per Claim By Airport" Map. 19

The map will be the last visual for our dashboard, so we are almost there.

STEP 1:

Before creating the map let's categorize "City" columns to get the accurate outcome.

  1.  Select "City" Column from the Airport Table
  2. Click On data category.
  3. Select City
  4. Do the same process for "Country" categorize as Country.
  5. Do the same process for "Name" categorize as Place.
  6. Do the same process for "State" categorize as State Or Province.

                    


STEP 2: Create the map.

  1. Double click on the  Map icon On the visualization bar.

  2. Map visual will display on the report.

  3.  Drag an drop the "Name" column from the Airport on the Location box.
  4. Drag an drop the "# Of Culmns" column from the TSA Claim Table on the Size box
  5. Drag an drop the ".Cost Per Claim" column from the TSA Claim on the Tooltips box.
  6. Drag an drop the "Location" column from the Airport on the Tooltips box.
  7. You should have a map like this bellow.



STEP 3: Configure the "Cost per claim & YoY by Airport" Visual

Part 1:

  1. Click on the Format icon.
  2. Fix the  Map  Size:     X Position: 0     Y position: 360         Weight : 660                    Height: 360
  3. Fix The Data Color:    Click on "Fx" Button      Than  change those fields bellow:     
  4. Fix the map control:   Turn Off Auto Zoom                        Turn on Zoom buttons.
  5. Fix the map style: Select "light".
  6. Fix The title: Type "Cost Per Claim By Airport"   . 
  7. Turn on the border :    Color : light grey   .
  8. Your should get a map like this bellow.       


     

STEP 4:  Create the legend

  1. Go to your data color.


  2. take screen shot of the color bar.       Save It.

  3. Select Insert

  4. Select Image and Load  the color bar.

  5. Select text Box 2 Times. Write "low" on the first  and  "High" on the second.

       Turn Off the background.  Font  default And Color default.

  6.  Align the picture and the high and low Text Boxes . You should get a legend like the one bellow.
